.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Lana-Del-Rey-BST-Hyde-Park@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Lana-Del-Rey-BST-Hyde-Park@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Lana-Del-Rey-BST-Hyde-Park@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Lana-Del-Rey-BST-Hyde-Park@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一名男子对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">拉娜德雷</a>发出死亡威胁后被捕。</p><p>根据<a href="https://montreal.ctvnews.ca/man-appears-in-quebec-court-to-be-charged-with-making-death-threats-against-lana-del-rey-1.6480388" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CTV 新闻</a>报道的一份起诉书，40 岁的丹尼斯·马利特 (Denys Mallet) 在 2022 年 1 月 1 日至 2023 年 7 月 6 日期间“故意威胁”这位歌手，造成死亡或身体伤害。</p><p>本月早些时候，他在德尔雷在加拿大魁北克音乐节上表演之前被捕。</p><p>此前，德尔雷因涉嫌偷了她的一辆汽车的一名男子而<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/lana-del-rey-granted-temporary-restraining-order-against-man-who-stole-her-car-3277792">获得临时限制令</a>。</p><p>早在 2018 年，一名跟踪她的男子被判处一年监禁后，这位歌手也发表了讲话。</p><p>今年 2 月，警方收到有关可能发生绑架的举报，当时 43 岁的迈克尔·肖恩·亨特 (Michael Shawn Hunt) 在距离佛罗里达州奥兰多安利中心演出一个街区的地方被拦截。 </p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3466945" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lana-del-rey-artist-live.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lana-del-rey-artist-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lana-del-rey-artist-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lana-del-rey-artist-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lana-del-rey-artist-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lana-del-rey-artist-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/lana-del-rey-artist-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2016年，一名男子也因闯入拉娜德雷的家被判处近三个月监禁。同年，这位明星获得了针对两名俄罗斯粉丝的限制令，据报道，这些粉丝威胁她并在公共场合对她尖叫。</p><p>在其他地方，这位歌手本周被发现<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/watch-lana-del-rey-work-a-shift-at-waffle-house-3471843">在阿拉巴马州的一家华夫饼屋轮班</a>。这位创作型歌手本周被发现在阿拉巴马州伯明翰的一家美国连锁餐厅分店提供咖啡。德尔雷扮演意想不到的新角色的视频片段和照片随后在网上分享。</p><p>在一段视频中，这位明星穿着蓝色华夫饼屋制服，戴着黄色名牌，从柜台后面给顾客递饮料。她还被拍到拿着风扇和使用咖啡机摆姿势。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/man-arrested-for-making-death-threats-against-lana-del-rey-3472165">男子因对拉娜·德雷发出死亡威胁而被捕的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
简·伯金 (Jane Birkin) 去世几天后，其家“成为小偷的目标” https://www.nme.com/news/music/jane-birkins-home-targeted-by-thieves-days-after-death-3472163?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jane-birkins-home-targeted-by-thieves-days-after-deathEmma Wilkes Sun, 23 Jul 2023 14:00:26 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3472163 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="简·伯金" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手兼演员于 7 月 16 日去世，享年 76 岁</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jane-birkins-home-targeted-by-thieves-days-after-death-3472163">简·伯金 (Jane Birkin) 去世几天后，其家“成为小偷的目标”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="简·伯金" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jane-birkin-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jane-birkin">简·伯金</a>在巴黎的家在她死后几天就遭到窃贼袭击。</p><p>这位歌手兼女演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/actor-and-musician-jane-birkin-has-died-aged-76-3469059">于 7 月 16 日被发现死亡</a>，享年 76 岁，这是她两年来独自在家的第一个晚上被她的照顾者发现的，当时她试图重新获得一些独立。柏金 (Birkin) 已与癌症生活了 16 年。</p><p>现在，当地媒体<a class="link " href="https://www.bfmtv.com/police-justice/jane-birkin-le-domicile-parisien-de-la-chanteuse-morte-dimanche-vise-par-une-tentative-de-cambriolage_AN-202307190289.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-ylk="slk:BFMTV;elm:context_link;itc:0" data-rapid_p="16" data-v9y="1"><em>BFMTV</em></a>报道称，周三（7 月 19 日）凌晨发生了一起未遂入室盗窃案。</p><p>该报援引警方消息称，凌晨 4 点前不久，伯金的一位儿时朋友住在家里，听到门后传来噪音。</p><p>据报道，警察被叫到现场，他们看到了试图闯入的潜在证据，包括门及其框架上的标记和损坏，以及散落在地上的木片。</p><p>此外，据称，在所谓事件发生的前一天，邻居看到三名男子试图进入房屋，并警告他们。 </p><figure id="attachment_3040142" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3040142" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3040142" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Jane-Birkin-Cannes-2021.jpg" alt="简·伯金 (Jane Birkin) 出席戛纳电影节" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Jane-Birkin-Cannes-2021.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Jane-Birkin-Cannes-2021-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Jane-Birkin-Cannes-2021-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Jane-Birkin-Cannes-2021-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Jane-Birkin-Cannes-2021-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Jane-Birkin-Cannes-2021-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3040142" class="wp-caption-text"> Jane Birkin 出席 2021 年 7 月的戛纳电影节。图片来源：Dominique Charriau/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>伯金的家人当天在一份声明中证实，她是自然死亡。她此前曾于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jane-birkin-doing-well-after-experiencing-stroke-3040103">2021年患过轻微中风</a>。</p><p>这位英法混血明星在电影和音乐领域享有悠久而卓有成效的职业生涯，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/serge-gainsbourg">塞尔日·甘斯布</a>保持着数十年的银幕内外关系。</p><p> 1969年，他们因共同出演法国电影<em>《Slogan》</em>而相识，并于同年发行了合作首张专辑。两人于 1980 年分手，柏金继续发行个人专辑并出演多部电影。</p><p>柏金包也是以她的名字命名的著名爱马仕手袋的灵感来源。爱马仕柏金包是市场上最昂贵的包包之一， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">Drake</a> 、Kris Kardashian、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">Beyoncé</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jennifer-lopez">Jennifer Lopez</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kate-moss">Kate Moss</a>等名人都拥有或收藏它们。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jane-birkins-home-targeted-by-thieves-days-after-death-3472163">简·伯金 (Jane Birkin) 去世几天后，其家“成为小偷的目标”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
